metadata.name: Rainy Night in Hong Kong
metadata.description:
An abstract/expressionist digital artwork, made from an original photo taken on a rainy night in Hong Kong. 

4000px x 5000px
300dpi.

**50% of profits from primary sales of this piece will be donated to Las Fotos Project** (or a non-profit/organization chosen by the collector).

*About Las Fotos Project*
[Las Fotos Project](https://lasfotosproject.org/) is a community-based nonprofit organization that inspires teenage girls & gender-expansive youth through photography, mentorship, and self-expression.
